room_title: Escape room "Fah-king Space Grail" by Nightwalker Caverns Escape Rooms in San Diego
room_description: A whimsical spoof on locating the Grail! Getting captured by aliens creates a feeling of dread and the urgent need to escape after players find themselves being transported through time. Players will engage in a scavenger hunt puzzle requiring they find the Grail to unlock their captors' space ship.
